---
layout: base.njk
title: Committee
description: Meet the Steering Committee and Organizing Committee for CAIS 2026 â€” the ACM Conference on AI and Agentic Systems.
permalink: /pages/committee/
extraStyles: |
    /* Committee-specific styles */
    .committee-photo {
        width: 100%;
        aspect-ratio: 1;
        object-fit: cover;
        filter: grayscale(100%);
        opacity: 0.9;
        transition: filter 300ms ease, opacity 300ms ease;
    }

    .committee-card:hover .committee-photo {
        filter: grayscale(0%);
        opacity: 1;
    }

    .committee-card {
        border: 1px solid var(--cais-border);
        background: var(--cais-bg-white);
        transition: border-color 200ms linear, transform 150ms ease, box-shadow 150ms ease;
    }

    .committee-card:hover {
        border-color: var(--cais-text);
        transform: translateY(-2px);
        box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(51, 58, 63, 0.08);
    }

    .committee-name {
        font-weight: 700;
        color: var(--cais-text);
        margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
    }

    .committee-affiliation {
        color: #666;
        font-size: 0.9rem;
        margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    }

    .committee-bio {
        font-size: 0.875rem;
        color: var(--cais-text);
        line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .role-badge {
        display: inline-block;
        background: var(--cais-accent);
        color: var(--cais-bg-white);
        font-size: 0.7rem;
        font-weight: 600;
        padding: 0.2rem 0.5rem;
        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: 0.5px;
        border-radius: 2px;
    }

    .steering-card {
        border: 2px solid var(--cais-accent);
        background: linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(255, 88, 32, 0.03), transparent 50%);
    }

    .steering-card:hover {
        border-color: #e64d1b;
    }

    .section-divider {
        border-top: 1px solid var(--cais-border);
        margin: 3rem 0;
    }
---

<!-- ===== HERO ===== -->
<header class="hero">
    <div class="container">
        <h1 class="display-5 fw-bold mb-3">CAIS 2026 Leadership Committees</h1>
        <p class="lead mb-0">The team responsible for delivering the inaugural ACM Conference on AI and Agentic Systems.</p>
    </div>
</header>

<!-- ===== STEERING COMMITTEE ===== -->
<section id="steering" class="py-5">
    <div class="container">
        <h2 class="section-title mb-2">Steering Committee</h2>
        <p class="lead mb-4">The Steering Committee provides strategic guidance and academic oversight for CAIS, ensuring the conference maintains the highest standards of scientific rigor and relevance to the compound AI systems community.</p>

        <div class="row g-4">
            {% for member in committee.steering %}
            {% set isSteering = true %}
            {% include "committee-card.njk" %}
            {% endfor %}
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<div class="container"><hr class="section-divider"></div>

<!-- ===== ORGANIZING COMMITTEE ===== -->
<section id="organizing" class="py-5">
    <div class="container">
        <h2 class="section-title mb-2">Organizing Committee</h2>
        <p class="lead mb-4">The Organizing Committee manages the day-to-day planning and execution of CAIS 2026, including program development, logistics, and community engagement.</p>

        <div class="row g-4">
            {% for member in committee.organizing %}
            {% set isSteering = false %}
            {% include "committee-card.njk" %}
            {% endfor %}
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- ===== GET INVOLVED CTA ===== -->
<section class="py-5 bg-light">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="cta-band p-4 p-lg-5 d-flex flex-column flex-lg-row align-items-lg-center justify-content-between gap-3">
            <div>
                <h2 class="h3 fw-bold mb-1">Interested in getting involved?</h2>
                <p class="mb-0">We're looking for reviewers, volunteers, and sponsors to help make CAIS 2026 a success.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
                <a href="mailto:{{ site.contact.email }}" class="btn btn-light btn-lg px-4 text-dark">
                    <i class="bi bi-envelope me-2"></i>Get in Touch
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
